-- =====================================================
-- TIMETABLE TEST DATA
-- For testing timetable management features
-- =====================================================
-- This file provides comprehensive test data covering:
-- - Weekly schedules for multiple classes and sections
-- - Multiple periods per day (8 periods)
-- - Subject assignments with teachers
-- - Room allocations
-- - Break/lunch periods
-- - Different schedules for different sections
-- =====================================================

-- Prerequisites: 
-- 1. Run academic_test_data.sql (for tenant, classes, sections)
-- 2. Run subjects_test_data.sql (for subject records)
-- 3. Run staff_test_data.sql (for teacher records)

